frames.caption: A couple stands closely under an umbrella on a rainy evening, illuminated by the warm glow of streetlights. The rain creates a shimmering effect on the umbrella and the wet street, enhancing the romantic atmosphere. They gaze into each other's eyes, sharing an intimate moment amidst the bustling city backdrop.
frames.description: The scene captures a romantic moment between two people under an umbrella on a rainy city street. The warm streetlights contrast with the cool rain, creating a cozy and intimate setting.

frames.caption: A couple stands closely under an umbrella on a rainy street, illuminated by warm streetlights. The man holds the umbrella, shielding both from the rain, while the woman looks down with a gentle smile.
frames.description: The scene captures a tender moment between two people on a rainy evening. The street is wet, reflecting the golden glow of the streetlights, creating a romantic and serene atmosphere.
